# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LeadIntel — environment variables
#
# The demo runs entirely on the in-browser MSW mock (no backend needed), so
# NONE of these are required to run `npm run dev`. They configure the optional
# production paths. Never commit real values — this file is an example only.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Public Supabase config (safe to expose; hardcoded fallbacks exist in code).
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR_ANON_KEY

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Bookings module (Calendly) — SERVER-SIDE ONLY (Vercel serverless functions).
# These are secrets: they must never appear in the frontend bundle or be
# prefixed with VITE_. They are read only by api/bookings/* on the server.
#
# Calendly Free plan has no webhooks and no programmatic booking, so the AE
# Meetings list is polled and the booking happens via the embedded widget.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
CALENDLY_API_BASE=https://api.calendly.com
CALENDLY_SYNC_INTERVAL_MS=120000          # 2 min default poll (client mirrors this)

# One block per AE (closer). Pick a short id for each AE (e.g. "dana") — it
# becomes the suffix of every var. The _EMAIL must be the closer's LOGIN email:
# that's how a logged-in closer is matched to their Calendly account + token.
# A user-scoped token only returns that user's own events.
# CALENDLY_PAT__DANA=<personal_access_token>          # secret
# CALENDLY_AE_DANA_NAME=Dana Whitfield
# CALENDLY_AE_DANA_URL=https://calendly.com/dana/30min
# CALENDLY_AE_DANA_EMAIL=dana@yourcompany.com
# CALENDLY_PAT__MARCUS=<personal_access_token>        # secret
# CALENDLY_AE_MARCUS_NAME=Marcus Lee
# CALENDLY_AE_MARCUS_URL=https://calendly.com/marcus/30min
# CALENDLY_AE_MARCUS_EMAIL=marcus@yourcompany.com

# Optional: lets the proxy join Calendly bookings to CRM leads server-side.
# SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<service_role_key>   # secret — server only
